<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11436</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>15469</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“史密斯侦探！”罗西挠了挠头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>15469</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17082</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他去哪儿了呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17082</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20719</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个狱警指了指监狱囚车。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20719</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>22720</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西飞过去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>22720</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>26721</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她看到史密斯侦探躲在车后面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>26721</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29222</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西皱起了眉头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29222</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>33219</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“您在做什么？我们得去抓巴布斯！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>33219</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37156</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>史密斯侦探咬了咬嘴唇。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37156</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41371</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你不要告诉任何人。我怕小丑。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41371</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>45621</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西吓了一跳。“真的吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>45621</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>48867</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“真的！”史密斯侦探说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>48867</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51619</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你能自己去抓巴布斯吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51619</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>54121</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西双手掐腰。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>54121</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>58340</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不会告诉任何人您怕小丑的，侦探先生。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>58340</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>62087</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，您得面对自己的恐惧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>62087</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65539</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>史密斯侦探叹了一口气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65539</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68225</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你说得对。你先走。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68225</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>71469</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我开着巡逻车跟你在市内见！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>71469</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74724</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好的，侦探先生，”罗西说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74724</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>76628</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“您一定要去哦。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>76628</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80663</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西飞走了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80663</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>87168</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她很快就发现了一辆小小的小丑车在市内开得飞快。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>87168</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90172</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>两辆警车跟在后面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90172</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>94920</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个小丑从小车的窗户伸出头来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>94920</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98172</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的头发绿得发亮。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98172</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>101421</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我再也不会回到那个肮脏的监狱了！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>101421</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105422</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你们听到了吗？绝对不会了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105422</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109172</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西的眼睛发射出激光。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109172</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>114668</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>嗞！那辆小车的一个轮胎爆了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>114668</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118174</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小车打滑，停下了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118174</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>122171</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那个绿头发的小丑从车里走下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>122171</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125922</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的夹克上别着一朵花。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125922</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>128923</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>另外一个小丑也下车了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>128923</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132671</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>接着还有两个小丑也下车了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132671</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138061</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那么小的车，他们怎么坐下的？”罗西想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138061</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141221</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>绿头发的小丑盯着罗西。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141221</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>143220</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“火箭女孩儿！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>143220</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148469</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我会把你送回监狱的，巴布斯！”罗西大声说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148469</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>151719</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们一伙都会跟着你进去的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>151719</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>155724</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>巴布斯哈哈大笑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>155724</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162471</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们怎么想？让那个小姑娘把我们送进监狱吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162471</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>164972</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>其他的小丑都笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>164972</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>167722</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“绝对不行，老大！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>167722</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>170969</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“监狱听起来太可怕了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>170969</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173386</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>巴布斯盯着罗西看。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173386</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177889</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你听到小丑们说的了吧，我们不去！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177889</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>182839</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他从口袋里拿出一个瓶子，按了一下按钮。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>182839</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>184818</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有液体喷出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>184818</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>190818</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西跳起来，液体射中了邮箱，邮箱被熔化了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>190818</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>194322</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“呃！”罗西咽了一口口水。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>194322</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>197072</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这个小丑真是可恶！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>197072</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>201469</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哈哈哈！”巴布斯坏笑着，再次按下按钮。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>201469</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>205469</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，再也没有液体出来了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>205469</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>211970</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“呃！用光了！”巴布斯把瓶子扔到地上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>211970</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>216831</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“别担心，老大！”另外一个小丑跑向小车，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>216831</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>220985</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“让火箭女孩儿领教一下这个！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>220985</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>224737</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他猛地打开后备箱。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>224737</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>229990</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西听到轰隆声和刺耳的摩擦声。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>229990</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>233485</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西吓得倒吸了一口气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>233485</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>238062</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>巨大的气球动物从后备箱跑了出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>